description: A skill that lets you learn more about giant pandas. Users can start by saying launch panda wizard and ask panda wizard to tell a fact about panda.
exampleInteractions: Alexa ask panda wizard to tell me a fact about panda
Alexa tell panda wizard to give me a panda fact
name: Panda wizard
shortDescription: Fun facts about giant pandas. We love pandas and want to learn more about pandas.
